Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.80,0:01:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村 緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.97,0:01:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經中午囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.33,0:01:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃飯的時間到囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.24,0:01:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！我在叫你啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.47,0:01:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要不理人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.38,0:01:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！痛死人了 ！\N頭髮被你拉掉五根了啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.31,0:02:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你不對\N不好好聽別人說話！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.18,0:02:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼\N故意挑林中小徑走啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.15,0:02:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定又想把我甩掉 是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.52,0:02:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是\N幹嘛趕得那麼急！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.29,0:02:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中餐也要吃呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.23,0:02:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不是故意挑這種路走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.80,0:02:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是比起折回原路\N直接破林而出會來得比較快罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.87,0:02:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傍晚 就可走出這個森林了 ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.70,0:02:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前\N我可沒休息的打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.97,0:02:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,午飯可以邊走邊吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.08,0:02:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 那我要吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.68,0:02:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.82,0:02:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不巧 我沒有帶任何吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.52,0:02:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔！但這個是我的\N我可不想與你分享
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.99,0:02:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.12,0:02:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 要是你告訴我\N蒼紫他們的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.86,0:02:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就分一點給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.96,0:02:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.43,0:02:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫他們現在在幹嘛呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.97,0:02:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十五話\N受控於志志雄魔掌下的村落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.34,0:03:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你說哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.48,0:03:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,般若君總是會照顧\N跟在蒼紫身後的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.05,0:03:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有好笑的大福\N胖胖的小太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死氣沉沉的阿明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.52,0:03:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都鬧在一起好不快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.79,0:03:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有蛇啊 危險 小心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.23,0:03:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我受夠了\N好心告訴你他們的事你卻……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.00,0:03:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我好好聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.63,0:03:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一句話都不說 亂無趣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.30,0:03:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才想緩和這凝重的氣氛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.21,0:03:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旅途上 大家快快樂樂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.61,0:03:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但就如我之前說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.68,0:03:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我一人被留在京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.48,0:03:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和大家共有的回憶\N只有那麼一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.82,0:03:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 蒼紫君卻\N永遠活在我的心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.42,0:03:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家現在都在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.22,0:03:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們離開我的時候\N我哭得好傷心……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.40,0:03:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 好好聽人家說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.70,0:04:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走路都比聽我說話來的有趣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.77,0:04:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你幹嘛特別花工夫\N把草叢撥到兩邊啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.41,0:04:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣才好走啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.52,0:04:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這小子要甩開我的話\N我一定沒轍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.72,0:04:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他竟為了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.49,0:04:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個性雖然完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不把內心表露出來的這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.56,0:04:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒跟蒼紫有點像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.96,0:04:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我改變心意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.80,0:04:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肚子很餓吧 緋村？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.13,0:04:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個小圓餅給你吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.34,0:04:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯一的一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.27,0:04:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了 唯一的一個！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.98,0:04:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？裏面會不會放毒藥啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才沒有呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.99,0:04:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村 剛剛好像有什麼聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.69,0:04:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保持安靜\N離我越遠越好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.29,0:05:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說有人要你的命\N莫非是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說了 快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.86,0:05:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕 現在被攻擊的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.13,0:05:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會牽扯到小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.17,0:05:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法\N只好來個先發制人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.54,0:05:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 等我啊！我……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.64,0:05:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可也是御庭派的一份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.44,0:05:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多少可以幫你一點忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.51,0:05:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.59,0:05:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人死了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒 但也快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.03,0:05:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有臨走前想說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.57,0:05:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你死前見到你\N也是一種緣份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼\N我都會盡力幫你完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.91,0:05:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜…拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.35,0:05:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將我弟弟和村民……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.92,0:05:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從志志雄一幫人手中救出來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.49,0:05:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.73,0:06:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這兒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.00,0:06:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 醒了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.21,0:06:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 我大哥呢 大哥……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.24,0:06:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們看到他時\N他已經…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.52,0:06:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畜牲 畜牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.69,0:06:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可不可以告訴我\N到底是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴你這個外人\N又有什麼用呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.33,0:06:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是為了會戰志志雄\N而朝京都走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.04,0:06:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我住在附近的新月村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.71,0:06:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二年前 \N志志雄的手下突然侵入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.88,0:06:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就殺了駐紮警官\N佔領全村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.98,0:07:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後又來了一個新警官\N也慘遭毒手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.59,0:07:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從此沒有一個警官敢來這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.35,0:07:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而志志雄的走狗\N一個個進駐村內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.66,0:07:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的新月村…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.17,0:07:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣被政府遺棄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.74,0:07:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被遺棄\N你說得太誇張了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.37,0:07:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們可能正在好好地擬定策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.28,0:07:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 這又怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.28,0:07:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是大哥從東京帶回\N最新的地圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.31,0:07:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看 已經沒有新月村了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.55,0:07:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥發現這一點\N覺得整村都怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.29,0:07:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是\N決定至少要保住自已的家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.06,0:07:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到就被殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是志志雄直屬部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.43,0:07:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是統治新月村的尖角\N那個王八干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.84,0:08:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不回村裏不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.41,0:08:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,村裏還有來不及逃走的爹娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.45,0:08:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥已死\N只有我可以救他們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.95,0:08:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大哥 請助我一臂之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.93,0:08:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我代替你大哥\N助你一臂之力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操\N這小子就拜託你囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.80,0:08:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.77,0:08:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 我一個人去就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.54,0:08:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在這等著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.98,0:08:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全毫無整頓\N如同廢墟一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.45,0:08:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄每半年會來這兒一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.06,0:08:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道他是為了什麼目的而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.56,0:08:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了迎接他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.06,0:08:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個村平常才都是由尖角管轄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.97,0:09:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次真巧 志志雄也來到村裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.11,0:09:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尖角要款待志志雄 \N現在應該在行館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.88,0:09:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要救出我爹娘的話\N只有趁現在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.92,0:09:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.35,0:09:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不靠近一點 會跟丟喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.19,0:09:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白癡 緋村可不是一般人唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.79,0:09:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再走近一點就會被他發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.13,0:09:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村這傢伙\N什麼事都一個人扛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.43,0:09:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是御庭派的出身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.63,0:09:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要幫你也是綽綽有餘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.45,0:09:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和那小孩的哥哥一樣\N全身被砍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.42,0:09:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是尖角搞的鬼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.46,0:10:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爹！娘！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.12,0:10:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這些外人\N不可讓外人活著回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.75,0:10:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼把他們殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.99,0:10:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小鬼一家人想從村裏逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.03,0:10:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了追究責任\N尖角大人才將他們處死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.47,0:10:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是把他們吊上去的是我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.04,0:10:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是…殺雞儆猴囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兒是偉大的志志雄陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.31,0:10:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從那些豬腦政府官手中奪來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.54,0:10:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這兒的生殺大權\N都操於志志雄陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.15,0:10:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和管理這兒的尖角大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尖角大人下令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.49,0:10:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外人只有死路一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.85,0:11:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.82,0:11:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該覺悟的是你們這些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.23,0:11:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平常我可不喜歡看人流血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是今天這個樣子\N我只得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.94,0:11:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺得你們一個不留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.69,0:11:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 振作一點嘛 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.89,0:11:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你很難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.50,0:11:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是現在可不是\N躲在一旁畏縮的時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.47,0:11:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼哭\N死人也不會活過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在趕緊振奮起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.34,0:11:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽我的話嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.14,0:11:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外人只有死路一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.58,0:11:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.51,0:12:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外人只有……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.18,0:12:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死路一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.40,0:12:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為那傢伙去京都了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.83,0:12:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到還在這兒混
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.87,0:12:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這名警官…是緋村的朋友嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.54,0:12:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.58,0:12:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.55,0:12:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼會在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.35,0:12:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工作呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.25,0:12:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在這兒的眼線告訴我\N志志雄現在人在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.09,0:12:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要等到討伐軍來到\N可能還要花些時日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.96,0:12:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才來附近晃一晃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.96,0:12:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我那名眼線現在下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.87,0:12:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那名少年的哥哥\N難道是警局的密探嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少年… 原來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.97,0:13:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三島榮一郎是新月村的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.51,0:13:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難怪毫不被懷疑的\N就能潛入村內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.98,0:13:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是身份曝光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.32,0:13:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才死命地要守住家人性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.95,0:13:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是笨蛋一個\N為什麼不等到我來……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.59,0:13:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  自已的部下死了 \N還說那種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.93,0:13:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你懂什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.78,0:13:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小臭鼬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.48,0:13:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去死啦\N殺死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.45,0:13:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我貫殺招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了啦\N他就是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.42,0:13:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟他計較那麼多\N可是沒完沒了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.69,0:13:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.87,0:14:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕快把屍體卸下來\N好好忌吊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.17,0:14:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.24,0:14:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.91,0:14:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可把屍體拿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.04,0:14:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.55,0:14:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說拿就拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.75,0:14:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬一冒犯了尖角大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.28,0:14:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們全村都不得好死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.92,0:14:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尖角大人沒有批准的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就維持原樣吊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡說些什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.82,0:14:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不是同鄉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.86,0:14:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們下場如此悲慘\N你們還對尖角千依百順
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反抗尖角只有死路一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.43,0:14:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不反抗他 尚可茍且偷生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.87,0:14:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想再把事情鬧大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.57,0:14:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了全村著想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.01,0:14:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這些外人和三島家的人\N現在就滾出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.01,0:14:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到了嗎 榮次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.22,0:14:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王八
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別動怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.06,0:14:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會賠上性命\N維護人的驕傲與尊嚴的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.13,0:15:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來就很少有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.90,0:15:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要茍延殘喘過一生的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.86,0:15:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪需要什麼驕傲、尊嚴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.50,0:15:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨你怎麼說\N你們外人是不會瞭解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.67,0:15:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不是因為你們這些警察沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.54,0:15:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.41,0:15:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正\N我不准任何人卸下屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.14,0:15:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們快給我滾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.28,0:15:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.17,0:15:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.50,0:15:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個村莊若是滅亡的話\N都是你們害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.15,0:15:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外人還敢說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.39,0:15:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.22,0:16:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個村子已經變成這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.26,0:16:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是志志雄理想中\N新時代的…日本嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.73,0:16:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類都害怕暴力\N在其統治之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.04,0:16:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有求生是唯一重要的事\N沒有驕傲、尊嚴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.57,0:16:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.84,0:16:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府當局真的放棄\N這個村落了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.35,0:16:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只這個村落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.31,0:16:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經有十個村落被遺棄\N而成了志志雄的領土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.32,0:16:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警局也不想再插手管事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.22,0:16:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不太懂啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.19,0:16:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 警察不行的話\N不是還有軍隊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.23,0:16:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨瓜 西南戰爭才開打半年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.06,0:16:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若出動軍隊鎮壓內亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.63,0:16:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我國內政之混亂\N會被各國摸得一清二楚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.37,0:16:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在可不是說那種話的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.04,0:16:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算想出兵\N也得不到官僚的首肯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.81,0:17:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.18,0:17:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都害怕\N大久保公卿的事件再度上演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.49,0:17:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府官僚也是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.25,0:17:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰不憐惜自己的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.66,0:17:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底有誰\N真能為我們做點事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.46,0:17:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰啊 誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.50,0:17:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道沒人真正關心這個村子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.06,0:17:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底有誰能讓這孩子一掃陰霾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.97,0:17:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的…我一個人來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.48,0:17:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再這樣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是村子 \N警方 軍隊 政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.85,0:17:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都會受控於志志雄的手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.52,0:17:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以此刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.16,0:17:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該是我和你這種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.73,0:17:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起替天行道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.93,0:17:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道志志雄的行館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.57,0:17:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒到京都那麼遠\N現在去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.54,0:17:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.24,0:18:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.61,0:18:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不能去 給我待在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.58,0:18:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.71,0:18:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也無法容忍\N幹出那種事的壞蛋呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.42,0:18:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.42,0:18:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.45,0:18:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管誰說什麼 我都要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.02,0:18:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我待在榮次的身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.24,0:18:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村拔刀齊那個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在箱根山頂時\N突然潛進森林中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.58,0:18:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才不小心跟丟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.15,0:18:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會再派人全力搜索的\N所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.05,0:18:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼處置呢\N志志雄陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.22,0:18:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 放過他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.82,0:18:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,半年沒泡溫泉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.89,0:18:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺真舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.89,0:18:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我還沒改變主意以前\N快把拔刀齊給我找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.00,0:19:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝主隆恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.77,0:19:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭喜你啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.87,0:19:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是下次再犯的話\N我可饒不了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.21,0:19:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.68,0:19:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瀨田大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.75,0:19:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了 什麼事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.02,0:19:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.55,0:19:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.06,0:19:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄陛下 志志雄陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.62,0:19:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煩死了 又怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.36,0:19:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脖子左邊帶有十字傷痕的男子\N和配帶日本刀的警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.40,0:19:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像正朝著我們的行館而來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.24,0:19:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.77,0:19:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還沒去登堂拜禮\N他們就先來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.27,0:19:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不愧是道上前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.58,0:19:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宗次郎 你出去迎接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.31,0:19:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,順便叫尖角隨時備戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.65,0:19:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尖角不管何時\N都處於備戰狀態呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.70,0:20:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.87,0:20:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你拿那個 要去哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去志志雄的行館\N我要報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.68,0:20:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼鬼話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不行的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.05,0:20:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是行不行的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是看你做不做而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.88,0:20:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我只有一個人\N才不會怕死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.19,0:20:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.32,0:20:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又怎麼了\N你要阻止我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.09,0:20:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭\N笨瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.99,0:20:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄的行館裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.33,0:20:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可不是只有尖角一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.46,0:20:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有志志雄的親信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.60,0:20:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然\N剛剛的蒙面部隊也會在那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.20,0:20:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你啊 還沒進去\N就給人家踢出來囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.64,0:20:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.07,0:20:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我決定要幫你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.61,0:20:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能感受你的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.38,0:20:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天若換成是御庭派的人被殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.42,0:20:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也會不顧性命去討血債的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.02,0:21:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉了 緋村\N我決定要幫這孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.06,0:21:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以跟著我\N但可別礙手礙腳的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.14,0:21:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們就是\N緋村拔刀齊和齊藤一吧

